thetank

DESCRIPTION

A simple tank-kills-enemies game.

GETTING STARTED

First, you should install python2 and pygame packages.
Then, the only thing you have to do is to type following lines in terminal:

cd thetank
cp thetank.py /usr/bin/thetank
chmod +x /usr/bin/thetank

USAGE

Just type thetank in terminal and press enter.
Use up, down, left and right keys to move (or W, S, A and D) and space to shoot fire. You can stop game by the Escape key or quit by the Q key.